Phase 3 — Build the agents

"In agents/orchestrator.py, create an Orchestrator class using the 
Anthropic Python SDK. It should take a research question, 
use Claude claude-sonnet-4-6 with tool_use to plan a 3-5 step research strategy, then sequentially call researcher.py, analyst.py, and writer.py agents, passing results between them. 
In agents/researcher.py, create a Researcher agent that 
connects to the MCP server tools and runs 3-5 web searches 
based on the orchestrator's plan, extracting content from the 
top results and saving notes. Use the MCP client from the mcp 
Python library to connect to the local server."